author: Allie Caren
title: WATCH: Frosting-faced toddler adorably denies he ate a cupcake
text:
Kids love to lie about eating sweets. Apparently, young Jack is no different .
“They were giving out free blue cupcakes in honor of the New York Giants,” his father, YouTube user Dave T. Koenig, wrote in a recent post . “Still not sure if my little boy managed to get himself one.”
>> Read more trending stories
Video still via Dave T. Koenig / YouTube An adorable viral video of Jack's denial has been viewed more than 830,000 times since it was uploaded Saturday.
